r maximum impact --- *This entertainment profile system transforms your systematic delivery into personality-matched content that entertains ... Please continue. Using Tool | Bash Command cp /home/user/personality_match_avatars/ENTERTAINMENT_PROFILE_SUMMARY.md /mnt/user-data/outputs/personality_match_avatars/ && echo \"=== ALL FILES IN OUTPUTS ===\" && ls -lh /mnt/user-data/outputs/personality_match_avatars/ && echo -e \"\\n=== TOTAL FINAL COUNT ===\" && find /mnt/user-data/outputs/personality_match_avatars/ -type f | wc -l View === ALL FILES IN OUTPUTS === total 184K -rwxr-xr-x 1 user user 14K Dec  3 22:43 AVATAR_ANALYSIS_SUMMARY.md ... -rwxr-xr-x 1 user user 80K Dec  3 22:43 IDEAL_CUSTOMER_AVATARS.csv === TOTAL FINAL COUNT === 4 Exit Code: 0 🎭 ENTERTAINMENT-ENHANCED AVATAR DATABASE COMPLETE! Your B2C Digital Offer Customer Intelligence System I've transformed your avatar database into a comprehensive B2C entertainment and personality intelligence system. Here's what you now have: 📊 ENHANCED DATABASE OVERVIEW 🎯 Main Enhancement: 50 Avatars with Entertainment DNA 6 NEW ENTERTAINMENT COLUMNS added to each avatar: Comedy Genre Preference - Specific shows/movies they connect with Humor Style Response - How they process and appreciate humor Entertainment Personality Match - Actors/characters they identify with Nostalgia Triggers - Cultural touchstones that resonate Hobby Interests Profile - Personal interests and activities Relatability Factors - Language patterns and pain points for copywriting 🎬 COMEDY GENRE DISTRIBUTION Top Entertainment Categories: Corporate/Executive Comedy (32%) - House of Cards, Succession, Veep, Mad Men Tech/Innovation Comedy (20%) - Silicon Valley, IT Crowd, Mythic Quest Analytical/Intellectual Comedy (18%) - The Big Short, Frasier, Monty Python Workplace/Process Comedy (16%) - The Office, Parks & Rec, Better Off Ted Financial/Investment Comedy (14%) - Wolf of Wall Street, Trading Places, Margin Call 💰 B2C PRICING STRATEGY BY ENTERTAINMENT TYPE